<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="initial-scale=1, width=device-width" />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;700&display=swap"
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <div class="text-content-title">
        <b class="title">Frequently Asked Questions</b>
      </div>
      <div class="subtitle">
        <p>Feel free to reach out on our</p>
        <a class = "discord">Discord</a>
        <p>if you have any more questions!</p>
      </div>

      <div class = "questions">
        <div class = "row">
          <div class = "box">
            <p class = "question">
              Who can participate?
            </p>
            <p class = "answer">
              Any students who are in grades 7-12 that live in British Columbia are allowed to participate! 
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class = "box">
            <p class = "question">
              How much does it cost?
            </p>
            <p class = "answer">
              Participation in Hack For Youth is completely free! 
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class = "row">
          <div class = "box">
            <p class = "question">
              What can I make?
            </p>
            <p class = "answer">
              A specific theme/prompt will be revealed at the hackathon. However, you are not required to follow the prompt and you could still win a prize!
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class = "box">
            <p class = "question">
              What do I have to bring?
            </p>
            <p class = "answer">
              please bring a laptop and charger. if you do not have a laptop, contact an executive on discord and we may be able to help you out.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class = "row">
          <div class = "box">
            <p class = "question">
              Will lunch be provided?
            </p>
            <p class = "answer">
              Yes! food, drinks, and snacks will be provided throughout the event to all participants for free.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class = "box">
            <p class = "question">
              Can I participate as a team?
            </p>
            <p class = "answer">
              Yes, we encourage participants to bring their friends along to form a team of 4 or less people.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class = "row">
          <div class = "box">
            <p class = "question">
              What are the prizes?
            </p>
            <p class = "answer">
              prizes will include gift cards, memberships to services, and more. You may also contact an executive on discord if you have any suggestions for prizes.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class = "box">
            <p class = "question">
              What if I can't code?
            </p>
            <p class = "answer">
              Don't worry! we encourage beginners to participate in Hack For Youth, there will be many mentors and guides to help; you may also recieve a prize for the best beginner project!
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
     
    </div>
  
  </body>
